---
---
<section class="products" id="productos">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Línea Premium</span>
      <h2>Elige tu detalle favorito</h2>
      <p>El verdadero cacao seleccionado a mano, transformado en piezas de colección para los paladares más exigentes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="products-grid">
      <article class="product-card">
        <div class="product-img">
          <div class="product-box">Caja Rosada<br/>Corazones</div>
        </div>
        <h3>Caja Rosada Corazones</h3>
        <p>Una selección fina de bombones de chocolate para expresar tus sentimientos.</p>
        <a class="card-action" href="https://wa.me/59179786916?text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20comprar%20la%20Caja%20Rosada%20Corazones" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Quiero este chocolate →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="product-card">
        <div class="product-img gold">
          <div class="product-box">Caja Surtida<br/>Rellenos</div>
        </div>
        <h3>Caja de Rellenos Surtidos</h3>
        <p>Una selección especial para sorprender con sabor, presentación y emoción.</p>
        <a class="card-action" href="https://wa.me/59179786916?text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20comprar%20la%20Caja%20Surtida%20de%20Rellenos" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Quiero este chocolate →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="product-card">
        <div class="product-img choco">
          <div class="product-box">Detalle<br/>Premium</div>
        </div>
        <h3>Estuche de Chocolates Premium</h3>
        <p>Un detalle sofisticado para regalar en cualquier momento u ocasión especial.</p>
        <a class="card-action" href="https://wa.me/59179786916?text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20comprar%20el%20Estuche%20de%20Chocolates%20Premium" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Quiero este chocolate →</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    padding: 92px 20px;
  }

  .products {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(217, 123, 168, 0.22), transparent 26%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #F9E7EF 0%, #FFF8FA 100%);
  }

  .container {
    width: min(1120px, 100%);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-head {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    color: var(--rose-wine);
    justify-content: center;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .eyebrow::before {
    content: "";
    width: 34px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--rose-wine);
  }

  .section-head h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 0.96;
    font-size: clamp(2.35rem, 5vw, 4.7rem);
    color: var(--berry-dark);
    letter-spacing: -0.045em;
  }

  .section-head p {
    margin: 18px auto 0;
    font-size: 1.06rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(42, 22, 18, 0.74);
  }

  .products-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .product-card {
    border: 1px solid rgba(122, 30, 77, 0.12);
    background: rgba(255, 248, 250, 0.72);
    border-radius: 30px;
    padding: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 55px rgba(122, 30, 77, 0.10);
    backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .product-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 28px 70px rgba(122, 30, 77, 0.16);
  }

  .product-img {
    height: 250px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 50% 30%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7), transparent 28%),
      linear-gradient(145deg, #F6D5E5, #C75C91 58%, #7A1E4D);
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.55), 0 18px 42px rgba(122, 30, 77, 0.18);
  }

  .product-img.gold {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 50% 28%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72), transparent 26%),
      linear-gradient(145deg, #FFF2C5, #D4AF37 54%, #7A4F10);
  }

  .product-img.choco {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 50% 28%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28), transparent 26%),
      linear-gradient(145deg, #7A1E4D, #4B0F2F 48%, #2A1612);
  }

  .product-box {
    width: 170px;
    height: 128px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    background: rgba(255, 248, 250, 0.32);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.42);
    box-shadow: 0 26px 50px rgba(42, 22, 18, 0.26);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    color: #FFF8FA;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 18px;
    line-height: 1.02;
  }

  .product-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--berry-dark);
    font-size: 1.42rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  }

  .product-card p {
    color: rgba(42, 22, 18, 0.72);
    line-height: 1.68;
    margin: 12px 0 0;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
  }

  .card-action {
    margin-top: 20px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    color: var(--rose-wine);
    font-weight: 800;
    transition: gap 0.2s ease;
  }

  .card-action:hover {
    gap: 12px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .products-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .products-grid {
      gap: 18px;
    }
    .product-img {
      height: 220px;
    }
  }
</style>
